  <summary date="2023-11-06T15:22:40Z" status="Introduced in House">USPS Subpoena Authority Act

This bill expands the administrative subpoena authority of the U.S. Postal Service.

Specifically, the bill authorizes subpoenas to investigate additional violations of law that involve the mail, including violations related to controlled substances.</summary>
